OL,3,CMillions with cars on finance could be
OL,4,Cdue payout amid mis-selling
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FIt follows the Financial Conduct
OL,8,FAuthority (FCA), the UK's financial
OL,9,Fwatchdog, investigation into claims
OL,10,Fsome consumers had been unfairly
OL,11,Fcharged inflated prices on new and
OL,12,Fsecond hand cars bought on finance.
OL,14,FBut how do you know if you've been
OL,15,Faffected?
OL,17,FBefore January 2021, some lenders
OL,18,Fallowed brokers (the person arranging
OL,19,Fthe loan, for example, a car dealer)
OL,20,Fto adjust the interest rates they
OL,21,Foffered customers for car finance.
