OL,3,CMillions with cars on finance could be
OL,4,Cdue payout amid mis-selling
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FTypically, the higher the interest
OL,8,Frate, the more commission the broker
OL,9,Freceived. This was known as a
OL,10,Fdiscretionary commission arrangement.
OL,12,FDiscretionary commission arrangements
OL,13,Fcreated an incentive for brokers to
OL,14,Fincrease how much people were charged
OL,15,Ffor their car loan ` and the FCA
OL,16,Fbanned this practice in 2021.
OL,18,FThe regulator has said there have been
OL,19,Fa high number of complaints about how
OL,20,Fmuch customers were charged before the
OL,21,Fban.
