OL,4,Cdue payout amid mis-selling
OL,5,Cinvestigation
OL,7,FMost of which have been rejected by
OL,8,Fproviders, spurring the investigation.
OL,10,FIf compensation is paid out, it's
OL,11,Fthought this could be as big as the
OL,12,Fmis-selling of PPI.
OL,14,FIf you took out a plan on a car or a
OL,15,Fvan before 2021, it's likely you could
OL,16,Fqualify for a payout.
OL,18,FMoney Saving Expert's Martin Lewis has
OL,19,Fsince issued advice for those who
OL,20,Fcould be impacted, calling on them to
OL,21,Fmake a complaint.
